/* Finder Styles for Eterno Verano */

/*

finder_body body element; contains all other elements
finder_header “Search for a product”
finder form element; contains search form
finder_brands “Results for Brand XYZ”
finder_table table of results
finder_thead table header of results
finder_tbody table body of results
finder_row_a table row; alternates between “a” and “b”
finder_row_b table row; same
finder_num table cell; result #
finder_dba table cell; Doing Business As; ie. “Corner Store ABC”
finder_map table cell; link to map of a store’s address
finder_miles table cell; miles from searched location
finder_address table cell; address of resulting location
finder_phone table cell; phone of resulting location
#finderMarkerLayer img can be used to alter the map pinpoints
vipcopyright table element; contains VIP logo and copyright;

we appreciate you keeping this visible

*/

